sentences: Charlie Cunningham (born 1984) is an English singer-songwriter and guitarist from Buckinghamshire.
He has released two studio albums, Lines (2017) and Permanent Way (2019).

In January 2017, Charlie Cunningham released his debut album, Lines on Swedish label Dumont Dumont, including lead single, "Minimum", to critical acclaim, and went on tour in Europe and North America later that year.
His second album, Permanent Way, was released in May 2019 on BMG.
